upload

public static File upload(java.lang.String filename,
                          org.openrdf.model.Resource subject,
                          java.io.InputStream is)
                   throws java.io.IOException
Upload a file into the upload folder, i.e. data/upload. In addition various metadata for the file is generate. In case the file already exists, and IllegalStateException with a meaningful error message is thrown. Typically this is directly handled in the Ajax servlet.
